  "texts": [
    "Some clarifications about this definition are in order.",
    "First, we must specify what 'doing the right thing' amounts to.",
    "I will say that, in a given situation where the morally relevant reasons are such that some but not all of the potential actions open to a system are morally acceptable, the system does the right thing iff it chooses one of the morally acceptable options.",
    "This presupposes that we have some way of determining which options are acceptable and which are not.",
    "This is of course a significant problem, which however is outside the scope of the current paper."
  ],
